{
  "id": "RAW_049043b4",
  "title": "Opus 4.6 Fast Mode 现已登陆 Vercel AI Gateway",
  "url": "https://vercel.com/changelog/opus-4-6-fast-mode-available-on-ai-gateway",
  "date": "2026-04-08 00:32:03",
  "author": "Walter Korman, Rohan Taneja, Jeremy Philemon, Jerilyn Zheng",
  "siteName": "Vercel News",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-customer-story=\"false\" class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-start gap-6 flex-initial article-module__XJFYTq__content\">\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Fast mode support for Claude Opus 4.6 is now available on AI Gateway.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Fast mode is a premium high-speed option that delivers 2.5x faster output token speeds with the same model intelligence. This is an early, experimental feature.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Fast mode's increased output token speeds enable new use cases, especially for human-in-the-loop workflows. Run large coding tasks without needing to context switch and get planning results without extended waits.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">To enable fast mode, pass <code>speed: 'fast'</code> in the <code>anthropic</code> provider options in AI SDK:</p>\n   <div class=\"flex flex-col items-stretch justify-start gap-4 flex-initial blog-code-block-module__TEKDOa__wrapper\">\n    <div class=\"relative code-block-module__NOThwW__wrapper blog-code-block-module__TEKDOa__codeBlock\" data-geist-code-block=\"\">\n     <button aria-label=\"Copy code\" class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__copyButton code-block-module__NOThwW__copyFloatingButton\" type=\"button\"></button>\n     <pre class=\"prism-code language-tsx code-block-module__NOThwW__pre blog-code-block-module__TEKDOa__maxHeight\"><code class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__code\" data-geist-code-block=\"true\"><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C05402c94-L1\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token imports punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token imports\"> streamText </span><span class=\"token imports punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">\"ai\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C05402c94-L2\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"display:inline-block\">\n</span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C05402c94-L3\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"> text </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">await</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token function\">streamText</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C05402c94-L4\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  model</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'claude-opus-4-6'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C05402c94-L5\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  prompt</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C05402c94-L6\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">   </span><span class=\"token template-string template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token template-string string\">Analyze this codebase structure and create a step-by-step plan</span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C05402c94-L7\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token template-string string\">    to add user authentication.</span><span class=\"token template-string template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C05402c94-L8\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  providerOptions</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C05402c94-L9\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    anthropic</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C05402c94-L10\" data-highlighted=\"true\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">      speed</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'fast'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C05402c94-L11\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C05402c94-L12\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C05402c94-L13\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></div></div></code></pre>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"text-center text-copy-14 text-gray-900\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">You can use fast mode with <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway/sdks-and-apis/anthropic-messages-api#configuring-claude-code\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway/sdks-and-apis/anthropic-messages-api#configuring-claude-code\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">Claude Code via AI Gateway</a> by setting <code>\"fastMode\": true</code> in your settings.json.</p>\n   <div class=\"flex flex-col items-stretch justify-start gap-4 flex-initial blog-code-block-module__TEKDOa__wrapper\">\n    <div class=\"relative code-block-module__NOThwW__wrapper code-block-module__NOThwW__hideLineNumbers blog-code-block-module__TEKDOa__codeBlock\" data-geist-code-block=\"\">\n     <button aria-label=\"Copy code\" class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__copyButton code-block-module__NOThwW__copyFloatingButton\" type=\"button\"></button>\n     <pre class=\"prism-code language-json code-block-module__NOThwW__pre\"><code class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__code\" data-geist-code-block=\"true\"><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C58387133-L1\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C58387133-L2\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token property\">\"model\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">\"opus[1m]\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C58387133-L3\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token property\">\"fastMode\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C58387133-L4\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></div></div></code></pre>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"text-center text-copy-14 text-gray-900\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Try fast mode directly in the AI Gateway playground for Opus 4.6.</p>\n   <div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 max-w-none not-frist:mt-20 not-first:mb-10 mx-0 max-[600px]:max-w-none max-[600px]:px-7 max-[600px]:[li_&amp;]:pr-14 max-[600px]:[li_&amp;]:pl-0 max-[600px]:w-full max-[600px]:mt-12 max-[600px]:mb-6\">\n    <img data-version=\"v1\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"900\" height=\"515\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"image-module__ssnYEW__intrinsic image-module__ssnYEW__lightMode\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcset=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F3b7Pw7DYHqiPCWgP7kcDV3%2F4aa9e8ce7ee404b029207b0745bc0315%2FCleanShot_2026-04-07_at_15.15.00_2x.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1x, https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F3b7Pw7DYHqiPCWgP7kcDV3%2F4aa9e8ce7ee404b029207b0745bc0315%2FCleanShot_2026-04-07_at_15.15.00_2x.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F3b7Pw7DYHqiPCWgP7kcDV3%2F4aa9e8ce7ee404b029207b0745bc0315%2FCleanShot_2026-04-07_at_15.15.00_2x.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\">\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Fast mode is priced at 6x standard Opus rates.</p>\n   <div class=\"scroller-module__6hSglq__overlayContainer text-module__qZtYrq__tableScroller scroller-module__6hSglq__isHorizontal\" data-geist-scroller=\"\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%\">\n    <div class=\"scroller-module__6hSglq__scroller text-module__qZtYrq__scrollerContainer\" data-geist-scroller-container=\"\" data-overflow=\"x\">\n     <div class=\"\">\n      <table class=\"text-module__qZtYrq__table\">\n       <tbody>\n        <tr>\n         <th>\n          <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Standard</p>\n         </th>\n         <th>\n          <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Fast Mode</p>\n         </th>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n         <td>\n          <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Input: $5 / 1M tokens\n           <br>\n           <span class=\"text-module__qZtYrq__lineBreak\"></span>Output: $25 / 1M tokens</p>\n         </td>\n         <td>\n          <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Input: $30 / 1M tokens\n           <br>\n           <span class=\"text-module__qZtYrq__lineBreak\"></span>Output: $150 / 1M tokens</p>\n         </td>\n        </tr>\n       </tbody>\n      </table>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">All standard pricing multipliers (e.g., prompt caching) apply on top of these rates.</p>\n   <a href=\"https://vercel.com/ai-gateway/leaderboards\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline flex flex-col items-center justify-start flex-initial inline-cta-module__jB83Xa__wrapper\"> \n    <div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row items-stretch justify-start gap-4 md:gap-6 flex-initial inline-cta-module__jB83Xa__content\">\n     <div class=\"flex flex-col items-stretch justify-start gap-1 flex-initial\">\n      <p class=\"text-copy-16 text-gray-900 inline-cta-module__jB83Xa__text\"><span class=\"inline-cta-module__jB83Xa__icon\"> \n        <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n         <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M0 1H0.75H5C6.2267 1 7.31583 1.58901 8 2.49963C8.68417 1.58901 9.7733 1 11 1H15.25H16V1.75V13V13.75H15.25H10.7426C10.1459 13.75 9.57361 13.9871 9.15165 14.409L8.53033 15.0303H7.46967L6.84835 14.409C6.42639 13.9871 5.8541 13.75 5.25736 13.75H0.75H0V13V1.75V1ZM7.25 4.75C7.25 3.50736 6.24264 2.5 5 2.5H1.5V12.25H5.25736C5.96786 12.25 6.65758 12.4516 7.25 12.8232V4.75ZM8.75 12.8232V4.75C8.75 3.50736 9.75736 2.5 11 2.5H14.5V12.25H10.7426C10.0321 12.25 9.34242 12.4516 8.75 12.8232Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n        </svg> \n       </span><strong>AI Gateway: Track top AI models by usage</strong></p>\n      <p class=\"text-copy-16 text-gray-900\">The AI Gateway model leaderboard ranks the most used models over time by total token volume across all traffic through the Gateway. Updates regularly.</p>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"flex flex-col items-start justify-center flex-initial md:ml-auto\">\n      <p class=\"text-label-14 font-medium inline-cta-module__jB83Xa__cta\">View the leaderboard</p>\n     </div>\n    </div> \n   </a>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\"></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Vercel AI Gateway 现已支持 Claude Opus 4.6 Fast Mode，为高端高频工作流提供 2.5 倍的输出速度，价格为标准版的 6 倍。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Vercel AI Gateway 现已支持 Claude Opus 4.6 Fast Mode，为高端高频工作流提供 2.5 倍的输出速度，价格为标准版的 6 倍。",
  "summary": "Vercel 宣布将 Claude Opus 4.6 Fast Mode 集成至其 AI Gateway。这一高级实验性功能在保持模型智能水平不变的前提下，输出 token 的速度提升了 2.5 倍。它专为对低延迟有严格要求的“人在回路”（human-in-the-loop）工作流和大规模编码任务而设计。此次更新包括对 Vercel AI SDK 和 Claude Code 的支持，并提供了一个用于测试的 Playground。不过，这种性能提升伴随着显著的成本增加，其定价为标准 Opus 费率的 6 倍。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Claude Opus 4.6 Fast Mode 可实现 2.5 倍的 token 生成速度。",
      "explanation": "这一实验性功能旨在解决对延迟敏感的任务，如实时编码辅助和复杂规划，且不会牺牲模型的推理能力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "与 Vercel AI SDK 和 Claude Code 无缝集成。",
      "explanation": "开发者只需在提供商选项中传递简单的 `speed: 'fast'` 参数，或更新 CLI 工具的 `settings.json` 文件，即可启用该高速模式。"
    },
    {
      "point": "卓越性能伴随 6 倍的价格溢价。",
      "explanation": "Fast Mode 的定价远高于标准费率（输入/输出每百万 token 分别为 30 美元/150 美元），定位为实现高价值生产力提升的专业工具。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "Fast mode 是一种高级高速选项，在保持相同模型智能水平的同时，提供 2.5 倍的输出 token 速度。",
    "无需切换上下文即可运行大型编码任务，无需长时间等待即可获得规划结果。",
    "Fast mode 的定价是标准 Opus 费率的 6 倍。"
  ],
